snippet.title: Lode Runner on Commodore PET levels 1-5
snippet.description:
I wrote a clone of the Apple II Lode Runner game for the Commodore PET. This is a run-through of levels 1-5. Check out the next five levels here: https://youtu.be/FAwI5WKqPO4

You can download the game, or play it online here at Norbert Landsteiner's PET archive: https://www.masswerk.at/pet/prgs/
